"      Cromolyn sodium (nasal): Drug information",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"drug drug_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?0/12/197?source=related_link\">",
"      Cromolyn sodium (nasal): Patient drug information",
